column3: Traffic;Phnom Penh: A man driving a RAV4 at high speed clipped the sidewalk
column4: hit a parked Starex and flipped his car over.------ The accident happened  at around 1.30 am on the east side of Wat Koh pagoda
column7: local authorities arrived and the RAV4 driver agreed to agree pay an undisclosed amount of compensation.------RASMEI
